<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a206200-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s6908"><num value="6908">§ 6908.</num><heading> Territorial participation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of State shall ensure participation in the Commission and its subsidiary bodies by American Samoa, Guam, and the Northern Mariana Islands to the same extent provided to the territories of other nations.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a206201-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/479/tV/s509">Pub. L. 109–479, title V, § 509</ref>, <date date="2007-01-12">Jan. 12, 2007</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/3643">120 Stat. 3643</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
